name: Max Ladabaum Jr. Death Certificate
description: "The value of art made by dead artists seems to be much larger than the value of art made by living artists. This trend is in bad alignment with the fact that money is useless when you are dead. I have decided to birth a new artist, named Max Ladabaum Jr., who will die next week." -Max Ladabaum Sr. (4/23/21)                 Art by Max Ladabaum Jr. is available at https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/tz/tz1NS3RofPoEdMMWuqdvRP4T48wwWUyfDT8Q
